<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men céng jīng xiāng yuē, xié shǒu zǒu guò qiān shān wàn shuǐ, wǒ men dōu yī tóng zǒu guò zuó tiān de kuáng fēng bào yǔ,
 wǒ men dōu mò mò láo zuò, yǒu guò nǐ dōng wǒ xī dào le shí hòu shén ràng wǒ men yòu xiāng jù yī qǐ,
 suì suì nián nián nǎ, qī pàn zài xīn lǐ, wǒ men dōu shì hǎo xiōng dì, wǒ men dōu shì hǎo xiōng dì,
 tóng kǔ gòng lè, dōu shì yī gè shēn tǐ jiān fù zhòng tuō zhēn chéng xiāng dài hé yī shì shén de xīn yì.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men céng jīng xiāng yuē 迦南367</title>
